modules.description: Provides functions to look up MIME types by filename extension and to list all registered extensions for a given MIME type. Works with strings representing file extensions and MIME type identifiers. Used to determine appropriate content types for HTTP responses or email attachments based on file names.

Provides functions to convert file extensions and filenames to MIME types, and to map MIME types back to associated extensions. Operates on strings representing file names, extensions, and MIME type identifiers. Used to determine appropriate content types for file handling or HTTP responses based on known mappings.

Provides functions to map file extensions to MIME types and vice versa. Operates on strings representing file names and MIME type identifiers. Used to determine appropriate content types for file uploads or to identify file formats from their MIME type.
